<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{لَنَهْدِيَنَّهُمْ سُبُلَنَا}</span> <span class="c4">[العنكبوت: ٦٩]</span> ،<span class="c5"> يَعْنِي:</span> سُبُلَ الْهُدَى، الطَّرِيقَ إِلَى الْجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> نَزَلَتْ قَبْلَ أَنْ يُؤْمَرَ بِالْجِهَادِ ثُمَّ أُمِرَ بِالْجِهَادِ بَعْدُ بِالْمَدِينَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> <span class="c3">{وَإِنَّ اللَّهَ لَمَعَ الْمُحْسِنِينَ}</span> <span class="c4">[العنكبوت: ٦٩]</span> ،<span class="c5"> أَيِ:</span> الْمُؤْمِنِينَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>